Dataset
Source: WORLD BANK GROUP вЂ“ IBRD Statement Of Loans and Guarantees - Historical Data : Approximately 1.5 million

Key columns include:

LOAN NUMBER
REGION
COUNTRY
BORROWER
LOAN STATUS
INTREST RATE
PROJECT NAME
PRINCIPAL AMOUNT
DISBURSED AMOUNT
BOARD APPROVAL DATE
END OF PERIOD DATE

Key Metrics:

Total Loans Analyzed, Total Loan Value, Loans Cancelled Amount, and Average Interest Rate(%)
Loan Cancellation Trends
Top Loan Countries
Loans By Region
Top Projects
Loan Utilization

Key Features:

End-to-end ETL pipeline using PySpark
Medallion architecture implementation
Snowflake-based data warehousing
Interactive Power BI dashboard

How to Run
Install dependencies:
pip install -r requirements.txt

Run ingestion:
python etl/data_ingestion/ingest_data_to_bronze.py

Run transformation:
python etl/bronze_to_silver/clean_loan_data.py

Run Star Schema Modeling:
python etl/silver_to_gold/transform_loans.py

Load data into Snowflake (Using Snowpipe) and execute SQL scripts.
python snowflake/run/snowflake_pipeline.py
python analytics/snowflake_pipeline.py

Open dashboard:
dashboard/IBRD_POWER_BI.pbix

